<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Batch 11 — T1 Drafts REBUILD — Mar 16, 2026</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-primary: #0f172a;
      --bg-secondary: #1e293b;
      --text-primary: #e2e8f0;
      --text-secondary: #cbd5e1;
      --green: #22c55e;
      --yellow: #eab308;
      --blue: #3b82f6;
      --red: #ef4444;
    }
    
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      color: var(--text-primary);
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    
    header {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bg-secondary);
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    
    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
    }
    
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .stat-value {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    
    .card {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
    }
    
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .badge-pass { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2); color: var(--green); }
    .badge-warn { background: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.2); color: var(--yellow); }
    .badge-info { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); color: var(--blue); }
    
    .contact-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    
    .contact-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    
    .contact-meta {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    
    .email-preview {
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--green);
      padding: 12px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }
    
    .qa-metrics {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    
    .metric {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
    }
    
    .company-section {
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--bg-secondary);
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    
    .company-header {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--blue);
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--bg-secondary);
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    
    .instructions {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--yellow);
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>🔄 BATCH 11 — T1 DRAFTS REBUILD</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>Mar 16, 2026 — Complete Rebuild</span>
        <span>51 Contacts × 8 Companies</span>
        <span>Formula: Corrected Para 1 + CTA</span>
      </div>
